Feature: Online Shopping Feature
  Verify if user is able to add product to cart and place an order in to the site

  Scenario: Login as a authenticated user
    Given user is  on homepage
    When user navigates to Login Page and enter username and Password
    And homepage is displayed 
    And user navigated to T-Shirt page
    And user selects a T-Shirt and product to cart
    And user navigate to cart page to proceed to checkout
    And user place an order
    Then success message is displayed
